article.headline: Texas St. 82, N. Colorado 59
article.story: SAN MARCOS, Texas -- Corey Jefferson scored 16 points, including four 3-pointers, and had five assists to help Texas State beat Northern Colorado 82-67 Tuesday night. Cameron Johnson and Brandon Bush each scored 14 points while Brent Benson added 11 points for Texas State (7-6). Devon Beitzel and Chris Kaba each hit 15 for Northern Colorado (5-11). Mike Proctor added 13 points and eight rebounds. Texas State scored the first nine points of the game and Northern Colorado never threatened. Texas State led 44-28 at the half.
